Uses of Package
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.xpath.ast

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.bpel.xpath.ast
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.convert.xpath This package contains classes which are used to convert xpath expressions from one version of BPEL to another. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.expr.xpath This package contains implementation classes for an expression parser and analyzer for xpath language.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.expr.xpath.ast.visitors This package contains some XPath AST visitors.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.xpath.ast This package contains the base classes for implementing a Jaxen based XPath Abstract Syntax Tree.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.xpath.ast.visitors
